    "description": "<strong>关注我们</strong><br>欢迎关注我们的官方社群：<br>《生命不是自动的》玩家Q群：559618269<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065720/extras/201c3e100e70b2e73c0836e3268ae599.poster.avif?t=1740983080\" width=620 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065720/extras/201c3e100e70b2e73c0836e3268ae599.webm?t=1740983080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065720/extras/201c3e100e70b2e73c0836e3268ae599.mp4?t=1740983080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>节奏？生存？<br>《生命不是自动的》可能可以说是一个timing 游戏。<br>玩家需要操纵角色的器官，让角色维持生命，并伴随她的一生。<br>生命脆弱，每一个失误都会导致主人公生病或死亡，操作好每个器官和每个选择，让主人公达成无病终老的完美人生。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065720/extras/bf0f23128dc619f945063c588847f5c2.webp?t=1740983080\" width=554 height=60 /></span><br>让你的手指在键盘上动起来，保持注意力，感受节奏，控制器官！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065720/extras/34fb6cf4a3b90a7f2a6b44dbf43dadf5.apng?t=1740983080\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065720/extras/34fb6cf4a3b90a7f2a6b44dbf43dadf5.poster.avif?t=1740983080\" class=\"bb_img\" width=347 height=177 /></picture></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065720/extras/afee3082b2e1a36c66a8224850aaaad7.poster.avif?t=1740983080\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065720/extras/afee3082b2e1a36c66a8224850aaaad7.webm?t=1740983080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store